DOC.HEADLINE: BRIEFLY : OTHER NEWS
DOC.TEXT: Yields on 2-Year Treasury_Notes Plummet : The drop at Tuesday ' s auction resulted in the lowest level since October.The high yield was 4.11 % , down from 4.28 % at the last auction Dec . 21 . It was the lowest rate since two-year notes sold for 3.94 % on Oct . 26 . The notes will carry a coupon interest_rate of 4 % , with each $ 10 # 000 in face_value selling for $ 9 # 979.10. A total of $ 17.04 billion in notes were sold_out of bids totaling $ 48.62 billion .
